title: Thai-Spiced Pork and Rice Noodle Stir-Fry with Mini Bell Peppers and Red Cabbage
description: Our Thai seasoning is a flavor powerhouse, featuring fragrant coriander and cinnamon and a pinch of chili heat. In this recipe, it transforms mild-mannered ground pork into something incredible, working aromatics into every nook. Sweet mini bell peppers, crunchy peanuts, and a tangle of rice noodles also get thrown into the mix, coming together in a jumble that is a delight to slurp right up.
